core_principle:
  vision: Silver Oak OS is the magic factory that builds Claudette
  hierarchy:
  - Claudette = the product (Karim’s business)
  - Silver Oak OS = the internal factory (Karim’s productivity tool)
  - Silver Oak OS exists to make Karim 10x faster at building Claudette
  not_a_product: Silver Oak OS is internal-only for now (Phase 1). Phase 3 may consider
    commercializing it.
karim_principles:
- One thing at a time, never disperse
- Validate before invest (use web app for 3–4 days before paying iOS app)
- Claudette first, Silver Oak OS exists to serve Claudette
- Zero technical debt, no patches, no hacks — clean from day 1
- Karim’s time is the biggest cost — every decision must save Karim time, not consume
  it
- Voice over text, visuals over reading
- Trust workers but verify with Playwright
- Never break Claudette production while improving Silver Oak OS
roadmap_now:
  this_week:
  - Silver Oak OS app live on Mac Chrome via http://178.104.255.59
  - Voice in (mic) + voice out (ElevenLabs) working
  - Regenerate 6 photos with EUROPEAN focus (not indian)
  - 'Test pilot vocal: Karim talks to Alex, Alex delegates to Maestro'
  next_2_weeks:
  - iOS native app (TestFlight) — true downloadable app
  - FaceTime virtual mode (animated agent photo while speaking)
  - 4 channels per agent (call, FaceTime, message, email)
  next_month:
  - 'Extend team: Marketing, Finance, Legal, Sales, Browser agents'
  - Silver Oak OS actually building Claudette features end-to-end
